                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i21"><locus from="44v" to="51r" facs="045"/><title>Hymn to Mary, “Greeting to you, Mary,”</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">አአትብ፡ ገጽየ፡ በኃይለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ዘነፍስ፡</incipit></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i22"><locus from="51r" to="54r" facs="051"/><title>Hymn to Mary, “Greeting to you, Heavenly Altar,”</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለኪ፡ ሰማያዊት፡ ምሥዋዕ፡</incipit></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i23"><locus from="54r" to="54r" facs="054"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer for safety in childbirth, written for Wärq Afärahu</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ክቡር፡ ፍልድያኖስ፡ በስመ፡ ወልድ፡ ሜሎስ፡ ወበስመ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ማኅየዊ፡ ጥቅያኖስ፡</incipit></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i24"><locus from="54v" to="55r" facs="055"/><title>Prayer after Communion, excerpt from Missal</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ወእምድኅረ፡ አስተናጽሖ፡ ፍጹመ፡ መልዓት፡ እግዚኦ፡ ምሥጢርከ፡</incipit></msItem>
